WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:05.629
Metro’s new ExpressLanes will operate 24
hours a day, 7 days a week on the

00:00:05.629 --> 00:00:12.250
I-110 Harbor Freeway between the 91 Freeway
and Adams Blvd in downtown Los Angeles and

00:00:12.250 --> 00:00:19.250
on the I-10 El Monte Freeway between I-605
and Alameda Street in downtown Los Angeles.

00:00:19.749 --> 00:00:25.499
Every motorist using the Metro ExpressLanes
is always required to have a FasTrak. Customers

00:00:25.499 --> 00:00:30.679
who already have a standard FasTrak can only
use the Metro ExpressLanes as a toll-paying

00:00:30.679 --> 00:00:35.890
customer. Customers who want the option to
travel as a toll-paying solo driver and/or

00:00:35.890 --> 00:00:42.500
a toll-free carpooler will need a new, switchable
FasTrak. The new Metro ExpressLanes FasTrak

00:00:42.500 --> 00:00:47.750
allows motorists to indicate the number of
occupants in a vehicle. A Metro FasTrak account

00:00:47.750 --> 00:00:54.750
can be opened in five convenient ways: Online
at metroexpresslanes (dot) net. At a Metro

00:00:55.329 --> 00:01:02.329
ExpressLanes Walk-In Center: One location
at 500 W 190th St, Gardena CA, 90248 (near

00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:10.480
the Harbor Gateway Transit Center) and another
at 3501 Santa Anita Avenue, El Monte, CA 91731

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:17.810
(at the new El Monte Transit Station). By
Mail by sending your application to Metro

00:01:17.810 --> 00:01:24.810
ExpressLanes, PO Box 3878, Gardena, CA 90247
By calling 511, or 877.224.6511 if you are

00:01:30.409 --> 00:01:36.380
outside of Los Angeles, Orange and Ventura
Counties. If you qualify for the ExpressLanes

00:01:36.380 --> 00:01:42.119
Equity Plan, you can open your FasTrak account
at a reduced rate by mail or at a Metro Express

00:01:42.119 --> 00:01:49.119
Lanes Walk-In Center. Promotional discounts
are offered by AAA. aaa (dot) com (forward-slash)

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:56.659
metroexpresslanes. For details and applications
please visit metroexpresslanes (dot) net Convenient

00:01:56.659 --> 00:02:02.859
FasTrak access and promotional discounts mean
more choices and more rewards for you. It’s

00:02:02.859 --> 00:02:03.659
about time.

